%% PROPOSED: Field Issue Cross-Team Resolution Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant FO as Field Operator
    participant Q as Quality
    participant HL as HW Lead
    participant HE as HW Engineer
    participant SWE as SW Engineer
    participant AE as Autonomy Engineer
    participant PE as Project Engineer
    participant ECO as Workflow 01 ECO Process

    FO->>Q: Report failure with serial and symptoms
    Q->>HL: Open FRACAS record and request triage
    HL->>Q: Confirm severity and containment needs

    par Hardware investigation
        HL->>HE: Analyze hardware evidence
        HE-->>HL: Return root cause findings
    and Software investigation
        HL->>SWE: Check software contribution
        SWE-->>HL: Return software findings
    and Autonomy investigation
        HL->>AE: Check autonomy contribution
        AE-->>HL: Return autonomy findings
    end

    HL->>PE: Recommend corrective action
    alt Design change required
        PE->>HE: Approve ECR creation
        HE->>ECO: Start Workflow 01 ECO
        ECO-->>PE: Return approved implementation package
    else Procedure or risk action
        PE-->>HL: Approve non-ECO action
    end

    PE->>Q: Request verification and effectiveness review
    Q-->>FO: Confirm field result
    Q-->>HL: Close FRACAS record
